WEBVTT

00:07.541 --> 00:09.343
‐ Previously on "The Betty
Broderick Story"...

00:09.343 --> 00:10.444
‐ I want to go
to Marriage Encounter.

00:10.477 --> 00:13.514
I love you and want to share
all that I am with you,

00:13.547 --> 00:15.516
but I also need
to be loved by you.

00:15.549 --> 00:17.451
‐ I've made many sacrifices,

00:17.484 --> 00:19.620
but I've made you sacrifice
as well.

00:19.653 --> 00:21.488
I want you to feel happy
and to know

00:21.522 --> 00:22.756
that it was all worth it.

00:22.789 --> 00:25.759
I hired an assistant,
Linda Kolkena.

00:25.792 --> 00:27.461
‐ Get rid of her
by the end of the month,

00:27.494 --> 00:28.529
or you can get out
of this house.

00:28.562 --> 00:30.364
‐ [scoffs]
You made a mistake.

00:30.397 --> 00:33.200
If anyone's gonna be
getting out, it's you.

00:33.233 --> 00:34.434
‐ [crying]

00:36.136 --> 00:38.705
‐ Yes, I'm a psychologist.

00:38.739 --> 00:41.875
I hold a PhD doctorate
in clinical psychology,

00:41.909 --> 00:44.511
and a diplomate in marriage
and family therapy granted

00:44.545 --> 00:46.613
by the American Board
of Psychology.

00:46.647 --> 00:50.717
My primary work is in
the treatment of families

00:50.751 --> 00:52.920
and couples.

00:52.953 --> 00:57.291
I'm frequently referred‐‐uh,
receive referrals from

00:57.324 --> 01:01.361
other psychologists,
psychiatrists, clergy.

01:01.395 --> 01:06.567
As one of my specialties
within couples therapy

01:06.600 --> 01:09.336
is the study of infidelity‐‐

01:09.369 --> 01:13.106
infidelity and its impact.

01:13.140 --> 01:15.242
[phone trilling]

01:15.275 --> 01:18.011
‐ Hi, Amy, it's Linda.

01:18.045 --> 01:23.050
I have Arthur Trafford
calling for Mr. Patterson.

01:23.083 --> 01:25.185
Of course.
Here he is.

01:25.218 --> 01:27.054
[pushes button]

