25:19.685 --> 25:23.188
What I'm doing to find a man.

25:24.423 --> 25:30.295
My dad, asking.

25:30.329 --> 25:34.967
My dad, who just wants
me to be safe,

25:35.000 --> 25:38.170
who is such a good person.

25:38.203 --> 25:42.074
